title: Fix problem with path extension during trip
message:
Fix problem with path extension during trip

pt-ml-pe -> pt-ml-ss -> pt-ml-sa would result in the program believing
the user is going in pt-ml-od direction (pt-ml-amarela) instead of
pt-ml-ap (pt-ml-vermelha), because somehow switching lines at pt-ml-mp
would be faster than doing so at pt-ml-ss. This fixes the problem by
not considering real-world length/time when extending paths, but just
the number of edges.
